Part 1

Using Pythia, simulate muons at 13 TeV

Output transverse momentum and psuedorapidity in the same C++ script

With PyROOT script, read the above data and plot using ROOT

---

Part 2

Calculate the fraction of accepted events over total events

---

Running the exercise

$ make getPythia

$ make simulation

$ simulation.job

$ python2 GetResults.py

$ make clean